{"tid":2488134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國驅逐艦明年服役，暫擬命名為「台北艦」","createTime":"2021-04-14T04:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T04:56:02.000Z","uid":52658,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"94ebbf8ad447618945a7be3e87b14e5b68cd883c","tid":2488134,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"解放軍海軍最先進的055型導彈驅逐艦，至今已有4艘下水舾裝，有4艘仍在分段建造中。<br />\n<br />\n有台媒近日報道指，該批驅逐艦中，有可能其中一艘會被命名為「台北號」，令未來可能出現「台北艦繞台」，甚至其與台灣的同名巡防救難艦在台海相遇。<br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒《中時電子報》指，按照解放軍海軍軍艦的命名原則，驅逐艦一般都以大中型城市作為名稱，多數會是省會城市<br />\n<br />\n而目前仍未有公開正式命名的省會城市，就只剩下廣西省南寧市、江西省南昌市、西藏自治區拉薩市以及中國僅法律上劃定的台灣省台北市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係唔知醜😪<br />\n日日係度跳腳瞎掰話台灣係自己既<br />\n就算叫多幾次 你都唔會收得返台灣架啦😪"},{"pid":"0b9a50c71ae1cc4d72cb9bac98f45a5fecfe61d3","tid":2488134,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"好肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f8bbca8f3368d68515d39becf55f8e912e7986","tid":2488134,"uid":117276,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"改定都好<br />\n遲下支那打輸<br />\n台灣接收呢隻軍艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cec17853a91896741d35d19e5bd4d8e4a1ab66","tid":2488134,"uid":52658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0b9a50c71ae1cc4d72cb9bac98f45a5fecfe61d3","tid":2488134,"uid":83582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:43:30.000Z","msg":"好肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係你改隻艦叫台北艦<br />\n人地就覺得台灣你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f2a31a5e61af318c96df5c0276a2d7ad7b42b9","tid":2488134,"uid":57005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime"